data.description: Fall in Love with this carefully updated corner lot Ocotillo home for Sale with PAID OFF SOLAR to take a bite out of your Energy bills! This 5 bedroom, 2 renovated bathroom home is Move-in Ready for you! You will love the Granite Counters, White Cabinets, Vaulted Ceilings, White Walls, Updated Bathrooms, Luxury Plank Flooring professionally installed throughout, Natural Gas Fireplace, 3 Car Epoxied floor Garage, and MORE. This home sits on an oversized Corner lot with PLENTY of Room for your Dream Pool!
